cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

The paper deals with the problem of automatic photo adjustment, which involves image processing and computer vision techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also extensively uses deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The use of deep learning also involves the formulation of the problem in a suitable way, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with image descriptors, which is a topic covered under cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper deals with the artistic enhancement of photos, which falls under cs.GR (Graphics).
